ks回應。<br />\n(If)上大學後，我要長跑全部奪冠。入樂團，校內。"},{"pid":"b23fde6ed8288a2486ba68640615d7fcc5e7fe19","tid":999223,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"中二病無得醫"},{"pid":"eba7f0be1e13f18413ebdb09ac6a2f8fc1aba54a","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9d43eac29a48ad70cb4c43ce997eceaa9be018","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"多少人，係『有刺地』恭喜我。 <br />\n表面上說恭喜我，其實有D背後 自己就好唔開心，葡萄我，風凉我，抹黑我。 <br />\n又唔 直接當口 同我講。 <br />\n普通朋友，咁樣做我可以理解，亦唔介意。 <br />\n因為 佢地只係 外人，不值一提。 <br />\n但我誓估唔到， <br />\n連 最好既知己 都係咁。 <br />\n4個男女知己當中， <br />\n就已經有1個係咁。 <br />\n你知唔知， <br />\n我有幾 心痛。 <br />\n我從未 睇低過你，從未 傷害過你。 <br />\n一直 當我係 人生中第3位 好既朋友， <br />\n點解 你要咁樣對我？"},{"pid":"f86cfc51b9a927055a43cf8846e238ad90aa7429","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"音樂老師由我DSE前叫我到DSE完結後，進她的樂團。 <br />\n但我一直也沒答應她，因為我嚮往是大型的樂團。 <br />\n我不會進中，小型樂團。"},{"pid":"6a1b3effde94e835644d2c93c640da2d75d0d5b7","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtSCSV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtSCSV0.png&h=bd5fd926&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4957c7e37f52d3cd6de1954e55982292b904df98","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/O8XKQpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO8XKQpP.png&h=98a35a4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"182a801bf61574f306435e30d654c9f2fcc56f97","tid":999223,"uid":179908,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.i